-- import: fifthtry/ft


-- ft.h0: `if`: Conditional Components

`ftd` supports a `if` to decide if the component should be visible or not, based
on the arguments, or global variables.


-- ft.code:
lang: ftd

\-- var dark-mode: true

\-- ftd.text: we are in dark mode
if: dark-mode

\-- ftd.text: light mode rules
if: not dark-mode